<para style="q1">

<verse number="3" style="v" />The enemy has pursued my soul;</para>

<para style="q1">he has pushed me down to the ground;</para>

<para style="q1">he has made me to live in darkness like those who have been dead for ages.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="4" style="v" />My spirit is overwhelmed within me;</para>

<para style="q1">my heart despairs.</para>
